        parsed_args={
            'prompt': 'What subscriber and usage metrics does the filing disclose? Specifically, what are the Starlink subscriber counts, revenue per user, ARPU, and any AI usage metrics like token consumption, API calls, or active users? How are these metrics defined and what comparability issues might they present? {{spacex_s1}}'
        }
